<title>USA: Applix Q4 oper shr $0.21 w/charge.</title>
<headline>Applix Q4 oper shr $0.21 w/charge.</headline>
<dateline>WESTBORO, Mass. 1997-01-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>(In thousands, except per share data)</p>
<p>				    Three Months	  Twelve Months</p>
<p>					  Ended		   Ended</p>
<p>				   Dec 31    Dec 31    Dec 31  Dec 31</p>
<p>					1996     1995     1996     1995</p>
<p>	Total revenues	  14,979   10,376    51,237  32,343</p>
<p> Operating (loss) income   (7,727)  (4,219)	 507   (662)</p>
<p> Net (loss) income	  ( 8,629) ( 3,163)  ( 2,636)     664</p>
